Package: DIBmix
Type: Package
Title: Deterministic Information Bottleneck Method for Clustering Mixed-Type Data
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Efthymios Costa, Ioanna Papatsouma, Angelos Markos
Maintainer: Angelos Markos <amarkos@eled.duth.gr>
Description: Implements the Deterministic Information Bottleneck (DIB) method
    for clustering datasets with both categorical and continuous variables.
    The package handles data preprocessing, feature selection, and clustering
    optimization using information-theoretic approaches.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: Rcpp, RcppEigen, stats, utils, np, rje
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RcppEigen
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
